sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server
Note left of browser: The user will submit the new note 
    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note
    activate server
    Note right of browser: After sending the new note, the server receives it and adds it,
    Note right of browser:  then sends the URL/for a reload of the page 
    server-->>browser: URL redirect
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/notes
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Page reload
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.css
    activate server
    server-->>browser: main.css
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.js
    activate server 
    server-->>browser: main.js
    deactivate server
note left of browser: Got both the css and the js
    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
    activate server 
note right of server: Request to get the list of notes
    server-->>browser: returns the content + the date
    deactivate server

    

   
